## 🧪 TESTING RULES

### Wajib ada test untuk:
- Semua kalkulasi risk score dan yield aggregation
- X402 payment flow (gunakan mock untuk blockchain calls)
- Semua API endpoints (happy path + error cases)
- Data normalization functions

### Struktur Test
tests/
├── unit/         # Pure functions, calculations
├── integration/  # API endpoints dengan database
└── e2e/          # Full flow termasuk X402

### Naming Test
```typescript
describe('calculateRiskScore', () => {
  it('should return HIGH risk when liquidity score below threshold', () => {})
  it('should return LOW risk when all factors are optimal', () => {})
  it('should throw error when required data is missing', () => {})
})
```

