## ⚛️ FRONTEND RULES

### Component Structure
components/
├── ui/              # shadcn components (JANGAN edit manual)
├── common/          # Reusable components (Button variants, etc.)
├── layout/          # Sidebar, Navbar, PageWrapper
├── dashboard/       # Dashboard-specific components
├── charts/          # Semua chart components
└── x402/            # Payment-related UI components

### Data Fetching Pattern
```typescript
// Selalu gunakan TanStack Query untuk server state
// Jangan fetch di useEffect langsung

// hooks/use-asset.ts
export function useAsset(id: string) {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: ['asset', id],
    queryFn: () => apiClient.get<AssetData>(`/v1/assets/${id}`),
    staleTime: 5 * 60 * 1000, // 5 menit
  });
}
```

### Color System — Nexus RWA Design Tokens
```css
/* Gunakan selalu dari design tokens ini, jangan hardcode warna */
--color-bg-primary: #0A0E1A      /* Deep navy background */
--color-bg-secondary: #0F1629    /* Card background */
--color-bg-tertiary: #1A2035     /* Elevated surfaces */
--color-accent-cyan: #00D4FF     /* Primary accent */
--color-accent-cyan-dim: #00D4FF33 /* Accent dengan opacity */
--color-accent-green: #00FF88    /* Positive/bullish */
--color-accent-red: #FF4444      /* Negative/bearish */
--color-accent-yellow: #FFB800   /* Warning/medium risk */
--color-text-primary: #FFFFFF    /* Heading text */
--color-text-secondary: #8892A4  /* Body text */
--color-text-muted: #4A5568      /* Muted/disabled text */
--color-border: #1E2A3A          /* Border/divider */
```

### Performance Rules
- Semua chart harus `dynamic import` dengan `ssr: false`
- Gambar wajib pakai `next/image`
- Gunakan `React.memo` untuk komponen tabel dengan data banyak
- Skeleton loading untuk semua data yang di-fetch

